<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Kate Ferdinand showed off her blossoming baby bump in a black bikini as she and husband Rio continued their sunshine break on Saturday.</p>

<p>The pregnant former TOWIE star, 29, took to Instagram to share a sweet snap of her cosying up to her football pundit beau, 41, admit their last-minute holiday before school starts.</p>

<p>Kate looked sensational in a black two-piece which featured a gold zigzag design, teaming her swimwear with a large straw hat and mirrored shades.</p>

<p>Yummy mummy: Pregnant Kate Ferdinand, 29, showed off her blossoming baby bump in a black bikini on Instagram as she and husband Rio, 41, continued their holiday on Saturday</p>

<p>The expectant mum flashed a broad smile as she posed with a shirtless Rio on an idyllic beach at their unknown holiday location.</p>

<p>Sharing her love for her partner, Kate simply captioned the snap: 'I love you.' </p>

<p>Clearly impressed with the photo, football ace Rio commented on the image with a complimentary remark - albeit about himself.</p>

<p>He penned: 'Looking STUNNIIIIIIIIIIIIING....in the black shorts', referring to his swimwear in the picture. </p>

<p>Hilarious: Clearly impressed with the photo, football ace Rio commented on the image with a complimentary remark - albeit about himself</p>

<p>The post comes days after Kate wowed fans as she posed in a floor-length light green silk dress which clinched her baby bump. </p>

<p>The shoulderless number featured spaghetti straps and showed off her tanned limbs. </p>

<p>Kate added to the glam with white strapped heels, a baby blue clutch and gold accessories.</p>

<p>While she wore her honey-blonde locks in waves around her features and held her bump proudly.</p>

<p>Stunning: The post comes days after Kate wowed fans as she posed in a floor-length light green silk dress which clinched her baby bump</p>

<p>Close: The day before, the blonde beauty looked radiant as she posed with her husband and his three children Lorenz, 13, Tate, 11, and nine-year-old Tia</p>

<p>She captioned the snap: 'Favourite photo spot... don’t be fooled by this pik, by the end of the night the feet were swollen, the heels were off and the bed was calling [sic].'</p>

<p>The day before, the blonde beauty looked radiant as she posed with her husband and his three children.</p>

<p>The former TOWIE star was every inch the glowing mum-to-be in a fitted bright yellow midi dress as two of her step-children cradled the blossoming bump. </p>

<p>Kate posed alongside Rio and her step-children Lorenz, 14, Tate, 11, and youngest Tia, in the unknown location as the family enjoyed time together before school re-starts.</p>

<p>Meanwhile Rio looked effortlessly cool in a grey t-shirt paired with matching trousers in the Instagram picture captioned: 'Family time'. </p>

<p>Sweet: Kate also shared another picture to her Instagram from the evening with her arm around Rio, captioned: 'My love'</p>

<p>Love: The beauty rested her hand on her growing bump as she beamed in the Instagram picture with her husband </p>

<p>Kate also shared another picture to her Instagram from the evening with her arm around Rio, captioned: 'My love'. </p>

<p>Earlier in the day Kate looked beautiful in a skimpy white bikini on Instagram which showed off her incredible shape. </p>

<p>She sat on a comfortable-looking sofa while looking out to sea as she shielded her face with a chic sun visor. </p>

<p>Kate wrote: 'One last trip before school starts ... the baby seems to like a holiday.' </p>

<p>'This baby seems to like a holiday': Kate shared a picture of her growing bump while wearing a skimpy white bikini on Instagram on Tuesday as she enjoyed a sunshine break</p>
